subject: Material for website
msgSnippet: Well, I m back from holiday. I still have to do some homework, but I managed to type together some text for a possible Quikscript website, as discussed
messageBody:
Well, I'm back from holiday. I still have to do some homework, but I managed
to type together some text for a possible Quikscript website, as discussed
earlier. Attached are the files. Also attached is another file I found in
this group too, which contains a lot of interesting information the site
could also use.

You may change the text I've written, my English is not as good as my Dutch.
Just give me proper credit.

The site can host the font, the original manual and some interesting links.

Perhaps someone is interested in re-writing the manual into a more
web-friendly format. I have found the manual rather sufficient.

Ewout
